   <standOff>
      <listAnnotation type="typednotes" xml:lang="nl">
         <note xml:id="note.d433e6189" type="dating">
            <p>Het jaartal 1897 is toegekend op basis van het journalistencongres dat op 1 augustus in Stockholm plaatsvond. Zoals het naschrift van de onderhavige brief vermeldt, was Israëls’ neef <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers051">Herman Louis Israëls</rs>, die dit congres bijwoonde (brief <ref target="ii40.xml">40</ref>), daar namelijk nog niet van teruggekeerd.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
      <listAnnotation type="typednotes" xml:lang="en">
         <note xml:id="note.d433e6246" type="dating">
            <p>The year 1897 has been assigned on the basis of the journalism conference that took place in Stockholm on 1 August. As Israëls writes in the postscript to the present letter, his cousin <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers051">Herman Louis Israëls</rs>, who attended this conference (letter <ref target="ii40.xml">40</ref>), had not yet got back from there.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
      <listAnnotation type="notes" xml:lang="nl">
